1
00:02:31,618 --> 00:02:32,607
Katya...

2
00:02:34,621 --> 00:02:37,613
Don't, you mustn't. It was all such a
long time ago, Georgia.

3
00:02:39,626 --> 00:02:42,288
Not for me, Katya.
Not for me.

